Global Macro Portfolio 




Designed for investors who desire a diversified absolute return investment and are willing to use shorting and leverage in an attempt to achieve a more attractive return/risk performance result:

Typically 20-25 long positions and 20-25 short positions, each up to 100% of capital
An additional 50% of capital may be invested in various hedging positions
Total gross leverage of up to 250%


